{"tid":1235310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔撚好再推民陣同伍展邦互片","createTime":"2019-06-17T06:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:56:44.000Z","uid":39752,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6dde2eda460f08bf962f9634252759c4d340eff","tid":1235310,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"無人咁撚得閒理佢哋鬧交，民陣搞事又好，伍展邦個底花又好，關我哋撚事？<br />\n理咗又點？有無嘢做到？無就唔好推，推咗只係阻住重要資訊<br />\n根本係狗咬狗骨兩派私怨嚟，就算唔幫襯呢兩派你重有大把律師選擇<br />\n我哋幾時咁撚熱心關心大台動向？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋只係剩返以一兩日計嘅時間可以話俾嗰二百萬人聽下一步要做乜<br />\n答唔出，做唔到，企撚咗喺度就會好似之前咁輸，唔會再有下一個五年</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">麥麥加推<br />\n香港就嚟輸，想贏就要有下一步</span></strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234257</a>"},{"pid":"5c52d2207653acab025eb37e4799f5fb6c610e77","tid":1235310,"uid":236140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"分化就玩完"},{"pid":"a0fa795f55216bb8b07e927247505a69c2505566","tid":1235310,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab32d37b7458b80739308c01683433d261eb898","tid":1235310,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd12ea493c1c74b6322800dc106353d28e28a62","tid":1235310,"uid":3876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"幫推依邊 我都唔再覆果兩邊直至有新既fact check證據"},{"pid":"551c9f179b4863a487aa90e879dfbaca3ce6324d","tid":1235310,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class